http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-smartphone h-12 w-12 text-green-success mx-auto" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="20" x="5" y="2" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M12 18h.01"></path></svg></div><div class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-slate-800 block mb-2">Dati Oltre la Clinica</strong>Si connette con dispositivi indossabili, app e dispositivi per fornire informazioni continue sul paziente.</div></div><div class="text-center"><div class="mb-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-brain h-12 w-12 text-teal-primary mx-auto" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 18V5"></path><path d="M15 13a4.17 4.17 0 0 1-3-4 4.17 4.17 0 0 1-3 4"></path><path d="M17.598 6.5A3 3 0 1 0 12 5a3 3 0 1 0-5.598 1.5"></path><path d="M17.997 5.125a4 4 0 0 1 2.526 5.77"></path><path d="M18 18a4 4 0 0 0 2-7.464"></path><path d="M19.967 17.483A4 4 0 1 1 12 18a4 4 0 1 1-7.967-.517"></path><path d="M6 18a4 4 0 0 1-2-7.464"></path><path d="M6.003 5.125a4 4 0 0 0-2.526 5.77"></path></svg></div><div class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-slate-800 block mb-2">Supporta Decisioni Migliori</strong>Profili, rapporti e tendenze sanitarie consentono trattamenti informati e personalizzati.</div></div><div class="text-center"><div class="mb-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-shield h-12 w-12 text-blue-accent mx-auto" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.5