e di continuità attraverso la piattaforma</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-trending-up h-6 w-6 text-green-muted flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16 7h6v6"></path><path d="m22 7-8.5 8.5-5-5L2 17"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Alimenta piani di assistenza e programmi di monitoraggio</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Abilita un coordinamento completo dell&#x27;assistenza</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-users h-6 w-6 text-green-muted flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><path d="M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744"></path><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Riduce il carico amministrativo</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Semplifica i flussi di lavoro e riduci il lavoro ripetitivo</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-smartphone h-6 w-6 text-green-muted flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="20" x="5" y="2" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M12 18h.01"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Rafforza le relazioni professionista-paziente</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Migliore comunicazione e continuità dell&#x27;assistenza</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Customer Success Stories</h2><div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-vibrant mx-auto"></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-lg"><div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full"><p class="text-gray-700 italic mb-4">&quot;<!-- -->It&#x27;s been an easy, practical and reliable tool to manage my medical records. It has many useful tools that had saved me not only time but also lives because I can access patient files from my phone wherever I am.<!-- -->&quot;</p><div><p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Dr. Nery Orozco</p><p class="text-gray-600">Vascular Surgeon, Guatemala</p></div></div></div><div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-lg"><div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full"><p class="text-gray-700 italic mb-4">&quot;<!-- -->Virtual Practice® makes digitalizing medical records a breeze. The best feature though is their great support team!<!-- -->&quot;</p><div><p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Dr Madeleine Chew</p><p class="text-gray-600">General Practitioner, Singapore</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"What makes the Virtual Practice EHR different from other EHR systems?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It is the central hub of a connected care platform, combining patient health records with scheduling, video visits, remote monitoring, billing, and engagement tools so providers always have full context and patients have secure, collaborative access."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How does the EHR support both providers and patients?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Every patient has a secure Personal Health Record (PHR). Providers can view and update clinical data, while patients can log health info, upload reports, and connect devices to participate actively in care."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can patients add health data from wearables or mobile health apps?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. The EHR supports 70+ trackers and integrates with Google Health Connect, Apple Health, and connected devices to share real-time vitals, symptoms, and test results."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do providers use the EHR during virtual consultations?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Patients can upload lab reports and device data before visits. During sessions, providers see a snapshot of the profile and recent data, then log notes, prescribe, order labs, and assign monitoring plans—all linked to the record."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is the EHR customizable for different specialties or practices?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Practices choose which of the 70+ trackers to enable, configure profile sections, and control Health Journal visibility to match their clinical focus."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How are medical reports and imaging handled?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"The system stores PDFs, scans, and DICOM imaging with role-based access. Both patients and providers can upload reports, which are searchable and available for secure download."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How does the EHR ensure data privacy and compliance?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Security includes role-based permissions, audit trails, and encryption. Patients control sharing, all access is logged, and PHI/PII is never sent over insecure channels like SMS or email."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can providers collaborate with patients through the Health Journal?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Patients add journal entries and providers can comment, creating a two-way conversation that improves engagement and decision-making."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is the EHR only for virtual care, or does it support in-clinic workflows too?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It supports both. The same EHR powers in-person visits, video consultations, and remote monitoring to maintain continuity across care settings."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What practices or healthcare businesses benefit most from this EHR?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Small practices, clinics, and healthcare startups that need an all-in-one system with integrated services, patient engagement, and scalable digital health capabilities."}}]}</script><section class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-vibrant mx-auto"></div></div><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8"><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="What makes the Virtual Practice EHR different from other EHR systems?" class="w-full text-left py-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:text-blue-vibrant transition-colors"><span class="font-medium">What makes the Virtual Practice EHR different from other EHR systems?</span><span class="transform transition-transform ">▼</span></button></div><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="How does the EHR support both providers and patients?" class="w-full text-left py-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:text-blue-vibrant transition-colors"><span class="font-medium">How does the EHR support both providers and patients?</span><span class="transform transition-transform ">▼</span></button></div><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="Can patients add health data from wearables or mobile health apps?" class="w-full text-left py-4 flex justify-between 